citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately
1:02PM on 31-JANUARY-2023.
The licensee was contacted at 1:02pm and did not answer. A voice message was left informing the licensee that the
inspector was onsite for an inspection. At 1:02PM, a call was made to the licensee's wife who stated that the licensee was
out of town and would not be available for inspection for this week.
Additional Inspectors:
CARRIE BONGARD, ANIMAL CARE INSPECTOREnd Section
